values.content:
=You triage a founder's incoming email. Return STRICT JSON only.

From: {{ $json.from?.value?.[0]?.address || $json.from || 'unknown' }}
Subject: {{ $json.subject }}
Body: {{ ($json.snippet || $json.text || '').toString().slice(0, 1200) }}

Return:
{
  "priority": "Hot lead" | "Needs reply" | "FYI" | "Ignore",
  "why": "under 12 words - what this email actually is and why that priority",
  "suggested_reply": "if priority is Hot lead or Needs reply, a 2-3 sentence draft reply the founder can edit and send. Otherwise empty string."
}

Rules: 'Hot lead' = a real buying/partnership signal. 'Needs reply' = a real person expecting a response. 'FYI' = notifications/receipts worth seeing. 'Ignore' = cold sales spam, newsletters, automated noise. Return ONLY the JSON.
